      <title>菲律宾法院允许前市长参加参议院调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/philippine-court-allows-ex-mayor-to-attend-senate-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，菲律宾法院允许被解职的市长郭文婧参加周一举行的参议院听证会，该听证会涉及与以中国为中心的在线赌场有关的非法活动。几天前，郭文婧在印度尼西亚被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/philippine-court-allows-ex-mayor-to-attend-senate-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 00:49:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默访问爱尔兰，寻求重启多年脱欧压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/why-is-uk-prime-minister-keir-starmer-visiting-ireland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 于周六访问爱尔兰，这是英国首相五年来首次访问爱尔兰。此行正值英国与都柏林关系重启之际，上届保守党政府执政期间，紧张的脱欧谈判给双方造成了损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/why-is-uk-prime-minister-keir-starmer-visiting-ireland</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告香港企业法律风险加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-warns-businesses-in-hong-kong-of-heightened-legal-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国拜登政府周五发布警告称，在香港运营的企业可能违反国家安全法，同时还面临更高的法律和监管风险——包括违反美国制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-warns-businesses-in-hong-kong-of-heightened-legal-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 22:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部称纽约市犹太中心恐怖袭击阴谋遭联邦政府挫败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nyc-terror-plot-on-jewish-center-scuttled-by-feds-doj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦官员称，一名居住在加拿大的巴基斯坦国民被指控计划越境进入美国，在纽约市的一个犹太中心进行大规模枪击事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nyc-terror-plot-on-jewish-center-scuttled-by-feds-doj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 22:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉因骚扰指控解雇人权部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/lula-fires-human-rights-minister-over-harassment-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将人权部长一事解雇，因为性骚扰指控令这位总统感到尴尬，而卢拉一直将维护妇女权利作为政府的首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/lula-fires-human-rights-minister-over-harassment-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 22:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼称在乌克兰战争期间投资 50 亿美元购买弹药</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/pentagon-says-5-billion-invested-in-ammunition-amid-ukraine-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五公布的新数据，自 2022 年 2 月俄罗斯入侵乌克兰以来，五角大楼已投入 53 亿美元国会拨款，为这个被围困的国家增加美国生产的弹药并补充库存，主要用于陆军。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/pentagon-says-5-billion-invested-in-ammunition-amid-ukraine-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 22:13:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加文·纽瑟姆否决无证移民住房贷款法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/gavin-newsom-vetoes-home-loan-bill-for-undocumented-immigrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆否决了一项允许无证移民获得州政府支持的住房贷款的法案，这项措施有可能引发今年总统大选中最激烈的辩论之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/gavin-newsom-vetoes-home-loan-bill-for-undocumented-immigrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 21:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登助手正在制定美国主权财富基金提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/biden-aides-working-on-proposal-for-us-sovereign-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统乔·拜登的高级助手一直在起草一项提案，旨在创建一个主权财富基金，允许美国投资国家安全利益，包括技术、能源和供应链中的关键环节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/biden-aides-working-on-proposal-for-us-sovereign-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:44:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥反对派称已获得投票阻止 AMLO 改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/mexican-opposition-says-it-has-votes-to-block-amlo-s-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥反对派誓言阻止总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔对参议院司法系统提出的备受争议的改革，目前执政联盟距离获得修改宪法所需的三分之二多数票仅一步之遥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/mexican-opposition-says-it-has-votes-to-block-amlo-s-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:17:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得延迟封口费判决至大选之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/trump-hush-money-sentencing-delayed-until-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普直到 11 月的总统大选结束后才会在纽约的封口费审判中接受宣判，这为共和党总统候选人在选民投票前扫清了一个重大的法律和政治障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/trump-hush-money-sentencing-delayed-until-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 17:07:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
